Subject: Re: [T2] front end alignment

The other issue is that sometimes your alignment issue is based on
suspension component wear which can be a safety issue. I last got a
front end alignment for $24. A good shop should be able to spot any
wear issues needing attention, especially if you ask them to check for
it.

John


